\begin_layout Description
Q: What versions of LyX are supported?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
A: At the moment the tool is very limited; it basically works for the author's
 machine, i.e.
 LyX 1.5.5 on Debian lenny.
 With some help the author plans to add support for more recent LyX versions
 (1.6) and a more thorough set of documents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Q: Why did you leave out my favorite feature 
\emph on
<insert random LyX command here>
\emph default
?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
A: In short, because I wasn't using it.
 Usually it is better to first aim for your own needs and then worry about
 others, or you will never get anything done.
 But if you know how to program in Python it should not be difficult to
 support other LyX features.
 If you don't you can always ask the author; you can find him at the elyxer
 gmail account.
